{"tid":2098370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「少圖」做愛問題","createTime":"2020-07-07T12:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T13:34:59.000Z","uid":56875,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8cbab40a56e90b2b2c28ee909ddc77908d7ce627","tid":2098370,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:25:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: right;\">我六十一歲，老公六十歲，結婚差不多一年。<br />\n我地拍拖兩年半，其實拍拖一年後已經好少做愛，結婚後基本上一個月一次，有時候兩個月一次。結婚後都是我主動，都係大概兩個月一次。我有提出呢個問題，每次佢都話會正視呢個問題，然而都無做過啲咩。究竟係我有問題定係我啲朋友搞得太多次？我同我老公連去到蜜月都係搞得幾次但係我哋放咗兩個月蜜月旅行，而每一次都係我主動，如果唔係我主動佢一早就瞓咗覺。<br />\n我哋兩個嘅關係其實都好好，佢都會成日攬我錫下我但係就係唔搞我。究竟其實我應該點？</div></strong></span>"},{"pid":"144664e0b610781e726f64298e2e34ce1aa0490a","tid":2098370,"uid":207574,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:27:30.000Z","msg":"離婚<br />\n圖就不必了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b90b7c101874259d1dcc0766d6b7bdfb5257d7","tid":2098370,"uid":105207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:27:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">日日話手足係condom<br />\n要接管晒手足的女人</span><br />\n會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#56875 - 人善被人J</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請保持批判性思考，善用「上一頁」和「不推文回覆」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">該會員以往言論 (5)：</div><code>1 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/fyDErT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/fyDErT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">分化</span><br />\n<code>2 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/fxtKzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/fxtKzT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>3 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/fxnxcT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/fxnxcT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>4 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/fxifnT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/fxifnT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />